Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Hannah Gray","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/hannah-gray","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/carol-bernard","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/carol-bernard","base_path":"/government/people/carol-bernard","content_id":"8c972115-3db4-4c96-862f-19f6454b6fc9","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Carol Bernard CBE","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62ac995b8fa8f5356b96ca69/s465_Carol_Bernard-NED-960x640px.png"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"1a83309b-6c2e-41af-adca-8b6fa92ce5f6","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":4,"started_on":"2022-09-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"60dacec7-9e8e-4445-9561-fb2a8e63fbe4","details":{"body":"<p>The Line Management Capability Programme focuses on raising the profile and esteem of line management by developing and setting the standards and requirements for line managers across the Civil Service. This transformational programme will improve employee experience for employees and managers and will inform the evolution of line manager training and development.  It will ensure the new standards are embedded across the Civil Service and integrated within the employee lifecycle.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-02T14:35:32Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Executive Director of Line Management Capability","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-02T14:36:02Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Carol Bernard CBE - Executive Director of Line Management Capability","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"52c02066-7c17-4a69-8e00-2b458e838b17","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2022-10-26T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":6864,"started_on":"2018-12-01T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"341d4b8d-158c-40df-b14d-7c84df5e8cf7","details":{"body":"<p>The Director of People and Places is responsible for Cabinet Office Human Resources and Estates. Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>managing the strategic estate requirements of the Cabinet Office, overseeing delivery partners in the Government Property Agency (GPA)</li>\n  <li>leading the design and implementation of the department’s locations strategy - a transformational people change programme to increase the presence of the department across regional and devolved locations</li>\n  <li>leading transformational reforms in the Department, such as the transition to smarter, hybrid ways of working</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-06-01T10:00:27Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director of People and Places","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-10-26T16:39:12Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Carol Bernard CBE - Director of People and Places","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"e5da25a9-e766-46c2-9cd4-d96b53088e00","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":7722,"started_on":"2022-06-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"f79cec2e-9c7a-4653-9f6b-4bdbd6b028d5","details":{"body":"<p>Carol Bernard joined the Government Property Agency in June 2022 as Non-Executive Director where she brings a wealth of change management and stakeholder engagement experience to the GPA Board.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-02T13:50:04Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-06-17T15:01:50Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Carol Bernard CBE - Non-executive Director","withdraw