</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The role of Chair oversees the work of the Agency by heading up the Board who set strategic direction and by providing expert property advice.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-03-11T10:39:41Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chair, Government Property Agency","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"5e6afab0-2e01-437f-ae1b-ed20a8214d6e","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-03T10:39:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"a7392675-e5a2-49d9-9723-05e6631f7705","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-03T10:38:57Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"11e9b882-9537-4835-859c-b214108808c2","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-03T10:40:16Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"5ce9516d-1b15-4a6a-a0f5-e6df9f41bdd8","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-03T10:37:49Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"2fc6c180-d8d7-4986-812f-9b02a1de113b","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-03T10:40:48Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"f79cec2e-9c7a-4653-9f6b-4bdbd6b028d5","details":{"body":"<p>Carol Bernard joined the Government Property Agency in June 2022 as Non-Executive Director where she brings a wealth of change management and stakeholder engagement experience to the GPA Board.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-02T13:50:04Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"f565d5d1-e0d4-4c8d-a098-a6a8176e54a9","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-08-21T14:25:21Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"7e1dc709-397d-4f96-8ce1-089183d24194","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Executive (CEO) is accountable to the Chair and the GPA Board for the strategic direction and performance of the GPA and to the Permanent Secretary of the Cabinet Office in respect of their Accounting Officer responsibilities.</p>\n\n<p>The CEO is responsible for the day-to-day management of the GPA, the efficient running, financial management, corporate governance and compliance, overall performance and strategic planning of the organisation.</p>\n\n<p>As Accounting Officer for GPA, the CEO is personally responsible for safeguarding the public funds for which they have charge.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-06-10T12:47:26Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive, Government Property Agency","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"f9457049-150e-4c90-b5dd-a38b7f22a660","details":{"body":"<p>Nick Brown joined the Government Property Agency (the GPA) in May 2022 as its Chief Financial Officer (CFO).</p>\n\n<p>Nick uses his experience gained in leadership roles, including a role he held at Magdalen College, Oxford as interim CFO, to support the continued evolution of the GPA into a best-in-class commercial real estate organisation.</p>\n\n<p>Nick works closely with the GPA’s CEO and Executive team to lead on its financial matters, improving return on investment and enhancing client satisfaction.</p>\n\n<p>Nick previously worked at M&amp;G Real Estate, where he held the same role, and brings more than 30 years’ experience in finance and property investment, development and management gained principally in the commercial sector.</p>\n\n<p>As CFO at M&amp;G Real Estate Nick led the multidisciplinary team that improved how the UK’s largest real estate investment fund for retail investors was valued and operated. This enabled it to keep delivering for its clients through the market turmoil after the Brexit referendum. Nick also reduced the number of go-to market franchises, which simplified the operating model, empowered franchise leaders and helped achieve growth targets.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-08-03T09:29:16Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Financial Officer","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"54dce7ad-72c3-4f6f-bce3-9bb195648d5e","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Financial Officer supports the continued evolution of the GPA into a best-in-class commercial real estate organisation.</p>\n\n<p>The CFO works closely with the GPA’s CEO and Executive team to lead on its financial matters, improving return on investment and enhancing client satisfaction.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-08-03T09:55:51Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Financial Officer","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA1255","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/government-property-agency","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/government-property-agency","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-property-agency","content_id":"e8ca4eeb-69b9-41f6-a6ff-971bf4dd0cb1","details":{"acronym":"GPA","brand":"cabinet-office","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/693c2e8